generated_story:
We changed lives for a day! Have you ever dreamed about swapping lives with someone else for a day? Perhaps you think it would be more fun to do something quite different for a change? We fixed it for four people - read how it went.

The four people came from different walks of life;

- Kati, a teacher;
- Krista, a dentist;
- Henri, a chef;
- Maija, a student.

We sent them to try a completely different profession for a day. Here’s how they all got on:

- Teacher Kati was transformed into a dentist, where she learned to fill a cavity. “When the drilling began, I found out it was louder than I expected! However, it was a great feeling to help improve someone’s health.”
- Dentist Krista got to learn from the best at a high-end restaurant. She had a chance to prepare tasty salmon in dill sauce and to get instructions on how to create a stunning presentation. "I was surprised by how calmly the chefs worked under pressure. I loved the way they created something beautiful from raw ingredients.”
- Chef Henri decided to try out teaching and helped a class of high-school students understand the importance of history. “It was a new challenge to try to make a topic like world history as interesting and entertaining as possible. It was fun to use my imagination to explain difficult subjects and I even discovered that I have a natural talent for it!”
- Student Maija had the chance to become a dental nurse for the day and help set up equipment, take patients’ details, and even serve tea
